.SH "NAME"
devm_mdiobus_alloc_size \- Resource\-managed \fBmdiobus_alloc_size\fR
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'struct\ mii_bus\ *\ devm_mdiobus_alloc_size('u
.BI "struct mii_bus * devm_mdiobus_alloc_size(struct\ device\ *\ " "dev" ", int\ " "sizeof_priv" ");"
.SH "ARGUMENTS"
.PP
\fIdev\fR
.RS 4
Device to allocate mii_bus for
.RE
.PP
\fIsizeof_priv\fR
.RS 4
Space to allocate for private structure\&.
.RE
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
.PP
Managed mdiobus_alloc_size\&. mii_bus allocated with this function is automatically freed on driver detach\&.
.PP
If an mii_bus allocated with this function needs to be freed separately,
\fBdevm_mdiobus_free\fR
must be used\&.
.SH "RETURN"
.PP
Pointer to allocated mii_bus on success, NULL on failure\&.
